Interface Label

All Superinterfaces:
org.nasdanika.common.Adaptable, BootstrapElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, HtmlElement, Item, org.nasdanika.ncore.Marked, org.nasdanika.persistence.Marked, org.nasdanika.ncore.ModelElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Subinterfaces:
Action, Link
All Known Implementing Classes:
ActionImpl, LabelImpl, LinkImpl
public interface Label extends BootstrapElement, Item
A representation of the model object 'Label'. Label is a text and an icon with a tooltip, notification badge, and help dialog. Labels can have children. Label is a base class for Link.

The following features are supported:

  • Id
  • Text
  • Icon
  • Tooltip
  • Outline
  • Notification
  • Children
  • Decorator
See Also:
  • AppPackage.getLabel()
